  <li>I have a fancy set of <a href="https://github.com/notwaldorf/.not-quite-dotfiles/blob/master/zsh/chrome#L15">aliases</a> like <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">make_</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">go_</code>, so that I donâ€™t have to
