<h4 id="2-adding-a-button">2. Adding a button</h4>

<p>Ok, so now Iâ€™m looking at <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">profile_chooser_controller.mm</code> and hereâ€™s how my brain would start nomming this code: that string ID is used in a button that
