â€œSettingsâ€ item in the hot dog menu (or hamburger menu, call it whatever food you wish) opens the â€œchrome://settingsâ€ tab. It will take some digging.</p>

<p>If you donâ€™t know how to use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ShowSingletonTab()</code>, I would <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">codesearch</code> again for different
